# AxiomCE — .gitignore

# --- Local-only sensitive data (Restricted class); never commit ---
private/
!private/.gitkeep

# --- Sensitive observation ingress: a candidate may be private BEFORE the
#     runner classifies it, so keep the whole inbox out of the tree (privacy
#     boundary at ingress). Keep the dir itself so `sync --watch` has a target.
inbox/observations/*
!inbox/observations/.gitkeep

# --- Runtime writer lock + atomic-write temp files (never commit) ---
runtime/writer.lock
private/runtime/writer.lock
*.tmp-*

# --- Never-store safety nets (should never be created, but block anyway) ---
*.pem
*.key
*.pfx
*.p12
*.env
.env
.env.*
*secret*
*credential*
*password*
id_rsa*
*.tax
*.tax.*

# --- Generated, disposable views ---
*.view.md

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Node / tooling ---
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# --- Scratch ---
*.tmp
*.bak
